9
00:00:32,670 --> 00:00:35,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I'll be on my way.</font>

10
00:00:35,470 --> 00:00:38,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Elise, I'll be in touch!</font>

11
