12
00:00:41,680 --> 00:00:44,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you intend to do now?</font>

13
00:00:44,550 --> 00:00:45,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

14
00:00:45,660 --> 00:00:49,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm afraid you got to see 
the absolute worst of all of us last night.</font>

15
00:00:49,710 --> 00:00:52,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure it left 
a very unpleasant impression.</font>

16
00:00:52,780 --> 00:00:57,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, we still do view you as family.</font>

17
00:00:57,710 --> 00:01:02,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes'm, indeedy. 
You're like a baby sister to us.</font>

18
00:01:05,450 --> 00:01:08,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So why don't we all stay together?</font>

19
00:01:10,320 --> 00:01:11,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

20
00:01:12,390 --> 00:01:16,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've all supported me 
through everything up until now.</font>

21
00:01:16,880 --> 00:01:19,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I think this is a good time
 for me to leave the nest.</font>

22
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:22,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

23
00:01:24,040 --> 00:01:26,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I promise to come see you.</font>

24
00:01:27,390 --> 00:01:31,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I want to be able to stand 
proudly on my own two feet.</font>

25
00:01:32,690 --> 00:01:34,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We will meet again.</font>

26
00:01:44,340 --> 00:01:45,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Arne.</font>

27
00:01:46,860 --> 00:01:50,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it true I was never human to begin with?</font>

28
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:54,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I never expected the mistress
to have already been bled.</i></font>

29
00:01:55,430 --> 00:01:59,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It appears she was already not human.</i></font>

30
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:03,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That must mean... 
From the very beginning...</font>

31
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:11,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">L-L-Lord Arne?</font>

32
00:02:11,630 --> 00:02:14,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You aren't carrying my blood after all.</font>

33
00:02:14,290 --> 00:02:16,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Huh?</font>

34
00:02:18,110 --> 00:02:19,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take a look in the mirror.</font>

35
00:02:21,140 --> 00:02:23,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! I have a reflection!</font>

36
00:02:23,340 --> 00:02:25,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How did it take you this long to realize?</font>

37
00:02:26,820 --> 00:02:31,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, whenever I drink your blood,
 it revitalizes me.</font>

38
00:02:32,210 --> 00:02:35,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Blood from animals and 
other species doesn't do that.</font>

39
00:02:35,670 --> 00:02:39,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In other words, you are definitely human.
 Both then and now.</font>

40
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:40,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, why...</font>

41
00:02:40,880 --> 00:02:44,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't understand it either. 
But does it really matter that much?</font>

42
00:02:44,790 --> 00:02:45,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

43
00:02:45,650 --> 00:02:47,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whether you're human or something else,</font>

44
00:02:48,410 --> 00:02:51,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you're still Lynn Reinweiß, correct?</font>

45
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:57,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As surely as you are Lord Arne.</font>

46
00:02:57,150 --> 00:02:58,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right.</font>

47
00:03:00,640 --> 00:03:04,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I believe I have fulfilled 
my contract with you, human.</font>

48
00:03:05,690 --> 00:03:08,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Mister Vampire.</font>

49
00:03:21,190 --> 00:03:23,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"With my beloved family."</font>

50
00:03:30,200 --> 00:03:31,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Father.</font>

51
00:03:33,010 --> 00:03:36,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What you did was very wrong, Father.</i></font>

52
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:42,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I know you still loved
 your family very much.</i></font>

53
00:03:43,540 --> 00:03:46,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And that's something I'll never forget.</i></font>

54
00:03:48,770 --> 00:03:52,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Everything I'd known 
changed for me that day,</i></font>

55
00:03:52,660 --> 00:03:55,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but that doesn't mean 
my story ended there.</i></font>

56
00:03:56,820 --> 00:03:58,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please allow me to stay here for a while.</font>

57
00:04:08,200 --> 00:04:10,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I became Lord Arne's assistant,</i></font>

58
00:04:11,290 --> 00:04:12,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>met many new people,</i></font>

59
00:04:13,260 --> 00:04:15,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and investigated lots of new cases.</i></font>

60
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:25,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's get going, Lynn Reinweiß.</font>

61
00:04:26,130 --> 00:04:27,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Coming.</font>

62
00:04:27,450 --> 00:04:33,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We still had many more days 
