122
00:07:55,400 --> 00:07:58,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said your name was Yurate?</font>

123
00:07:58,010 --> 00:08:00,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean your lover
 tried to kill you?</font>

124
00:08:01,140 --> 00:08:05,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was fast asleep one night
when Hanna suddenly assaulted me.</font>

125
00:08:05,790 --> 00:08:09,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I fought back without thinking
and accidentally killed her.</font>

126
00:08:10,320 --> 00:08:12,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You <i>killed</i> her?</font>

127
00:08:13,110 --> 00:08:14,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mm-hmm.</font>

128
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:17,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So who was this Hanna?</font>

129
00:08:17,700 --> 00:08:19,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A human girl.</font>

130
00:08:19,810 --> 00:08:24,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She was so kind and charming,
and also a bit of a crybaby.</font>

131
00:08:24,390 --> 00:08:27,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But anyway, I happened 
to save her life one time.</font>

132
00:08:46,630 --> 00:08:47,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh no!</font>

133
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:02,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you alive?</font>

134
00:09:04,110 --> 00:09:04,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

135
00:09:10,510 --> 00:09:12,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The first time I saw her, I could tell...</i></font>

136
00:09:13,310 --> 00:09:18,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>we were destined to meet
 in the ocean that day.</i></font>

137
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:21,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>After that, we became inseparable.</i></font>

138
00:09:36,580 --> 00:09:39,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We had both been all alone before.</i></font>

139
00:09:39,010 --> 00:09:40,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You were alone?</i></font>

140
00:09:40,690 --> 00:09:43,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'd gotten separated from my pod.</i></font>

141
00:09:43,280 --> 00:09:45,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't really know what Hanna's deal was,</i></font>

142
00:09:45,940 --> 00:09:48,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but she said she could never go home again.</i></font>

143
00:09:58,240 --> 00:09:59,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ouch.</font>

144
00:10:10,500 --> 00:10:12,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Every day with her was so much fun.</i></font>

145
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:16,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We were only together 
for a short while, though.</i></font>

146
00:10:20,220 --> 00:10:21,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't it lovely?</font>

147
00:10:21,240 --> 00:10:24,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like a real summer romance!</font>

148
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:26,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So why did Hanna attack her?</font>

149
00:10:26,520 --> 00:10:28,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No deductive reasoning necessary.</font>

150
00:10:28,870 --> 00:10:31,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The woman was probably after 
the mermaid's flesh and blood.</font>

151
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:35,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Flesh and blood?</font>

152
00:10:35,400 --> 00:10:37,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, her flesh and her blood.</font>

153
00:10:38,300 --> 00:10:42,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When humans eat mermaid flesh,
 they become immortal.</font>

154
00:10:42,160 --> 00:10:44,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because of that, 
many humans hunt mermaids.</font>

155
00:10:44,860 --> 00:10:47,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But not her. Hanna was different!</font>

156
00:10:47,580 --> 00:10:50,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, she swore eternal love to me.</font>

157
00:10:50,270 --> 00:10:53,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eternal? Even though 
human life is so short?</font>

158
00:10:53,750 --> 00:10:59,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe she was just promising to love her
and stay with her until the day she died!</font>

159
00:10:59,010 --> 00:11:03,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, then perhaps she decided 
to kill her out of love?</font>

160
00:11:04,370 --> 00:11:05,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kill her...</font>

161
00:11:06,560 --> 00:11:09,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and make Yurate hers forevermore?</font>

162
00:11:09,840 --> 00:11:11,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't understand what you mean!</font>

163
00:11:11,810 --> 00:11:13,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's probably something like that.</font>

164
00:11:13,770 --> 00:11:19,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe she wanted to stuff and mount 
the dead mermaid to keep her forever.</font>

165
00:11:19,610 --> 00:11:21,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your reasoning is too sloppy!</font>

166
00:11:21,640 --> 00:11:25,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If she'd meant to kill her from the start, 
she'd already had plenty of chances.</font>

167
00:11:26,560 --> 00:11:29,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">True. And even if it was
 just for a short time,</font>

168
00:11:29,290 --> 00:11:32,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">there was probably no need 
to start living together.</font>

169
00:11:33,690 --> 00:11:34,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll take the job.</font>

170
00:11:35,640 --> 00:11:38,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll kill some time, at the very least.</font>

171
00:11:39,680 --> 00:11:44,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That night, I was sleeping 
