172
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:58,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hanna?</font>

173
00:11:59,780 --> 00:12:00,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

174
00:12:05,280 --> 00:12:06,200
